# TASK_PACKET

Task ID
CRUSHR-FORMAT-06

Title
Add file-manifest checkpoints to improve recovery completeness verification

Role
BUILDER

Objective
Introduce a file-level manifest layer that allows salvage to determine:

1) whether a file is fully recoverable
2) whether a recovery is partial but ordered
3) whether a recovery is incomplete and must remain partial
4) whether a file can be recovered anonymously without path metadata

This packet builds directly on FORMAT-05 self-identifying blocks.

